PrecisAppointment of ROZA ARONOVITCH, of Ottawa, Ontario, as a full-time member of the Canada Labour Relations Board to hold office during good behaviour for a term of five years; and order that ROZA ARONOVITCH be deemed to be employed in the Public Service for the purposes of the Public Service Superannuation Act, effective October 2, 1995.
